<dl id="n40109a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40109a">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40109a"> 109(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ peau pour / peau </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: When Satan approached God a second time, he said, &ldquo;Skin for skin. <font color="green">[French <i>peau pour peau</i>]</font>, yea, all that a man hath will he give for his life. But put forth thine hand now, and touch his bone and his flesh, and he will curse thee to thy face&rdquo; (Job 2:4-5). </mm> </dd></dl>
